OL,7,FThere are calls for a public inquiry
OL,8,Finto the pregnancy drug DES after a
OL,9,Fyear-long ITV News investigation
OL,10,Fexposed the scale of the medical
OL,11,Fscandal, Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,12,FSarah Corker reports
OL,14,FHundreds of women who were exposed to
OL,15,Fa now-banned drug given on the NHS,
OL,16,Fdubbed "the hidden thalidomide", are
OL,17,Flaunching a campaign for a public
OL,18,Finquiry and compensation, after a year-
OL,19,Flong ITV News investigation exposed
OL,20,Fthe scale of the medical scandal.
