OL,7,FStilbestrol, commonly known as DES,
OL,8,Fwas a synthetic hormone prescribed to
OL,9,Fan estimated 300,000 women on the NHS
OL,10,Fbetween the 1930s and 1980s to treat
OL,11,Fseveral issues, including miscarriage,
OL,12,Funtil it was linked to rare cancers
OL,13,Fand infertility in the children of
OL,14,Fthose who took it.
OL,16,FMore than 300 victims have formed DES
OL,17,FJustice UK following ITV News'
OL,18,Freporting, which highlighted the
OL,19,Ffailures of the health authorities to
OL,20,Fact on safety warnings about the
OL,21,Fdrug's sinister side effects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
