OL,7,FIn a significant development, the
OL,8,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,9,Fsaid he has asked NHS England to
OL,10,F"urgently work closely with local
OL,11,Fcancer alliances" to ensure that GPs
OL,12,Fare aware of the impact of DES and to
OL,13,Fmake sure "those who could benefit
OL,14,Ffrom additional screening aren't
OL,15,Fmissing out".
OL,17,FMary Stuart, 83, was prescribed DES
OL,18,Ftablets by doctors in Newcastle in
OL,19,F1966 for six months after suffering
OL,20,Fmultiple miscarriages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
