OL,7,FHer daughter Helen Scanlan, now 58,
OL,8,Fwas born the following year, but it
OL,9,Fwasn't until she was a teenager that
OL,10,Fdoctors started to realise the harm
OL,11,Fthat the drug had caused.
OL,13,FMary Stuart, 83, tells ITV News she
OL,14,F'lives with guilt', wishing she'd
OL,15,Fnever taken the DES tablets she was
OL,16,Fprescribed while pregnant with her
OL,17,Fdaughter Helen, who has suffered a
OL,18,Flifetime of health issues
