OL,7,FHelen began to suffer from
OL,8,Fdebilitating pain from the age of 14
OL,9,Fonwards. In her 20s, she was diagnosed
OL,10,Fwith a misshapen womb and later
OL,11,Fcervical cancer.
OL,13,F"The pain just got so bad that we
OL,14,Fagreed the best thing was to have a
OL,15,Ffull hysterectomy to take away all the
OL,16,Fdanger and risk," she told ITV News.
