OL,7,F"I'm still in pain now, 20-plus years
OL,8,Flater. It's now also the worry of what
OL,9,Felse goes wrong, and they said when I
OL,10,Fhit menopause, that would be the next
OL,11,Fdanger time.
OL,13,F"I'm devastated that I haven't had a
OL,14,Ffamily of my own; my two sisters have
OL,15,Fgot children, but I haven't. I'm very
OL,16,Flucky that I have a stepdaughter, who
OL,17,FI adore, but I do feel like I've
OL,18,Fmissed out a lot."
