OL,7,F"She really suffered, and I was
OL,8,Fdevastated," Mary said. "It's just
OL,9,Fwhat I've lived with for the last 50-
OL,10,Fplus years; I've always thought I
OL,11,Fcaused Helen's problems.
OL,13,F"I didn't know. I took the tablets
OL,14,Fwillingly because they said I would
OL,15,Fhave a better chance of keeping the
OL,16,Fbaby. I was advised to take it, and I
OL,17,Ftook the advice.
OL,19,F"I've regretted it ever since, but I
OL,20,Fcan't turn the clock back, I've got to
OL,21,Flive with it," she added.
