OL,7,FSome gynaecologists are now calling
OL,8,Ffor those guidelines to be urgently
OL,9,Fchanged to include annual screening.
OL,11,FDr Wael Agur, consultant
OL,12,Fgynaecologist, told ITV News the
OL,13,Fscreening programme "needs to be
OL,14,Fexpanded".
OL,16,F"The current screening arrangements
OL,17,Fwould pick up the standard type of
OL,18,Fcancer, the common types of cancer,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
