OL,7,FAlongside a public inquiry,
OL,8,Fcampaigners are calling for an
OL,9,Finformation campaign to ensure
OL,10,Fhealthcare professionals are aware of
OL,11,FDES, medical research into the long-
OL,12,Fterm, intergenerational effects of the
OL,13,Fdrug, targeted screening for cancers
OL,14,Fand fertility issues and a
OL,15,Fcompensation fund.
